! Diagnostics

Real-time detection of unbalanced wikitext tokens.

!! Features

* ''Token balance checking'': Detects unclosed or mismatched markup
* ''Live updates'': Checks as you type (with debounce)
* ''Visual warning'': Shows badge with unbalanced tokens

!! Checked Tokens

!!! Symmetric (must appear in pairs)
* `''` (bold)
* `//` (italic)
* `__` (underline)
* `~~` (strikethrough)
* `^^` (superscript)
* `,,` (subscript)
* ``` `` ` `` ``` (code)

!!! Asymmetric (open/close pairs)
* `[[` / `]]` (links)
* `{{` / `}}` (transclusion)
* `<<` / `>>` (macros)

